    "en": {
      "title": "Arrested Tamil Nadu fishermen in Karainagar sea area",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Local Police Magistrate Court has ordered that the 06 Tamil Nadu fishermen who were arrested at the Karainagar beach in Jaffna should be remanded till the 15th.",
        "Six of the fishermen who set out to catch fish from Jagathapatnam Fisheries Department in Pudukottai District of Tamil Nadu were caught by the Navy yesterday Monday while they were encroaching into the Sri Lankan waters and engaged in fishing.",
        "The 06 Tamil Nadu fishermen who were arrested were produced in the District Magistrate's Court today through the officials of the Water Resources Department.",
        "After that, the judge ordered the 06 fishermen to be remanded until the 15th."
      ],
